    <section id="how" class="section">
      <h2>How I built this</h2>
      <p>This page is a Markdown file (with HTML) plus a CSS file. To reproduce:</p>
      <pre class="code-block"># create repo and push
git init
git branch -M main
git remote add origin https://github.com/swara2013/swara2013.github.io.git
# add files
git add index.md assets/style.css
git commit -m "Add site with fancy layout"
git push -u origin main</pre>
      <p>GitHub Pages will serve the repository at <a href="https://swara2013.github.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://swara2013.github.io</a>.</p>
